<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">就算化石本身不大，<delay8 />
也会给人一种饱含历史的感觉。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中充满了太古的浪漫气息啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">这个房间里展出的化石
大多是海中的生物，<delay20 />换句话说，
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />这里就像是水族馆一样啊！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">说起化石来，<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也算是略知一二啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想，<delay20 />这里展出的化石<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />差不多是几亿年前的东西吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">难以想象如此巨大的生物<delay8 />
曾经竟然在地表上横行无忌啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是充满了古代的浪漫气息！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这些家伙<delay8 />
看起来都不太好惹啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想长得跟它们一样威风。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这巨大的体型正是它们的魅力所在啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想是你的话，
应该能理解吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我原本还以为<delay8 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />化石都是几亿年前的东西，<delay20 />
但其实也有年代比较近的化石哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过所谓比较近，<delay8 />
也要追溯到几千几百万年前了。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我变成化石的话应该是这种感觉吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="10" />的头部！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="10" />的身躯！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把我挖掘出来的时候，<delay8 />
可要尽量保持完整啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">在这个房间里看到的骨架<delay8 />
感觉都挺眼熟的啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说是这么说，<delay20 />
我也从来没见过<delay8 />化石以外的骨头就是了！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊哈哈哈！</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么样？<delay20 />
有看到<delay8 />喜欢的化石吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />尽情欣赏吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">情侣<delay8 />一般不太会来这里，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以像我这样喜欢独来独往的人，<delay8 />
也能静下心来欣赏化石。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />古老的东西该怎么说呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特别令人怀念，<delay20 />
给人以一种闲寂之感啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">化石这种东西，<delay20 />
可以靠着它寻到各种生物的根源，<delay8 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是看着就心潮澎湃啊。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不如我借着散步，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />时不时来<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />看看<delay8 />
有没有增加新展品吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话说回来，能建成<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可真是一件可喜可贺的大好事。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到这间房间，<delay8 />
总有一天会摆满帅气的化石<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～！<delay20 />我就止不住地激动啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多亏了<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />开张，<delay8 />我们才有机会轻而易举地
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欣赏到化石，<delay8 />真令人高兴啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<delay20 />你有注意到地上的图案吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />1根1根的线条<delay8 />组成连结古今的树状图，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是暗藏玄机啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>